    <item>
      <title>华夏幸福的债券投资者仅获得部分付款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/china-fortune-land-s-bond-investors-get-only-partial-payment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，华夏幸福美元债券的部分持有者已收到债务重组协议中 12 月 31 日到期付款的不到三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/china-fortune-land-s-bond-investors-get-only-partial-payment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 02:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港机场首次发行40亿港元本币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/hong-kong-airport-prices-first-local-currency-bond-with-a-hk-4-billion-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着金融中心客流量的恢复，香港机场管理局将发行首支本币公共债券，债务交易定价为 40 亿港元（合 5.12 亿美元）。]]></description>
