    <item>
      <title>股市延续新年疲软，美元稳定：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着大型科技股的下跌，华尔街的冒险情绪消退，亚洲股市跟随美国股市和国债的下跌而下跌。美元继续上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 22:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市、债券齐跌，创数十年来最差开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/stocks-bonds-drop-in-tandem-for-worst-start-to-year-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们希望年底泛市场反弹能够在2024年的第一个交易日继续上涨，但他们却得到了相反的结果，这一交易日股市和债券出现了开年以来最严重的一致下跌之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/stocks-bonds-drop-in-tandem-for-worst-start-to-year-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:40:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美联储的疑虑，美元以 3 月份以来最好的一天拉开 2024 年的序幕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/dollar-kicks-off-2024-with-best-day-since-march-on-fed-rethink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员减少了对美联储 2024 年降息规模的押注，美元以 3 月份以来的最大单日涨幅拉开了新年的序幕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/dollar-kicks-off-2024-with-best-day-since-march-on-fed-rethink</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
